Her father named her Rosaline, a beautiful name. But he hated her, because she killed her mother.
&ldquo;Little Frank wasn&rsquo;t like that,&rdquo; her grandmother would tell her much later. &ldquo;After your mother died while giving birth to you, my little Frank began drinking. He drank away his fortune, his everything&hellip;&rdquo;
When he was drunk, he would beat her for no real reasons. Once she used a few crayons she got from her art lessons to draw something on a wall in the living room while he was not at home.
